data.description: Dreaming of your own home on an acre of gorgeous land, in a quiet neighborhood yet still located near the city. It is possible! At 1322sqft & Boasting an inviting floor-plan w/hardwood floors, newer bath, remodeled kitchen & plumbing, center island & pantry. Fresh paint & new ceiling fans throughout. The attached garage converted to 3rd Bedroom w/brand new carpet & door to outside. The sunroom offers wood beam ceilings, used year-round to enjoy the tranquil setting & views of the .9 acre lot. Outside features a freshly tilled fenced-in garden, ready to plant, chicken-coop, fire pit, shed & country views. A New well 2021, water filtration system installed 2022, New A/C in 2023. Septic cleaned 2023. Plumbing & electric updated 2013. The New driveway 2023, leads to oversized 2.5+car garage w/12x16 addition on the back, a wood-burning stove, insulated garage door & a newly installed opener. Perfect for the hobbyist or car enthusiast. Wiring already in place for a generator.
